{"tid":524344,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"儲錢諗住交學費比呀媽叫我拎哂啲錢出黎","createTime":"2018-01-09T13:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T05:56:20.000Z","uid":90802,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"571d355d842eba4924aee7d96efb2b283f1e08e7","tid":524344,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:19:12.000Z","msg":"hd仔黎 黎緊升上degree要交學費 要20萬<br />\n呀媽有3層樓（未計而加住緊）係手 但冇諗住幫我出住少少學費<br />\n其實冇咩所謂 都咁大個人啦 自己學費啲野自己比返好天經地義<br />\n啱啱出黎做野幾個月 先儲到萬幾蚊 <br />\n返工帶飯又冇乜娛樂 啲錢都係交下電話費同Netflix<br />\n交下屋企雜費同換咗幾部好舊嘅電器<br />\n幾個月糧主要都用哂係屋企到 <br />\n買比自己最貴嘅都係千二蚊手錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先呀媽就叫我比1萬蚊佢 要裝修佢間房<br />\n佢話間房舊 但其實唔舊 3/4年前先裝修完 入面啲傢俬好新淨 <br />\n咁我就答冇必要裝修 而且我要儲錢交學費 <br />\n之後佢就發脾氣話我冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日收工仲買咗蛇羹去佢舖頭到<br />\n咁孝順係冇乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係你地會點對住呢個老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11553e581cf0b102081f8f2477688baf99ba428","tid":524344,"uid":4139,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:19:57.000Z","msg":"叫你老母仆街死啦"},{"pid":"be2145367fe3f6f665271ee371906c08e964cd65","tid":524344,"uid":7878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"你有細佬？"},{"pid":"443f2095221fc3e6d54e5f6937b973f55eae2bc7","tid":524344,"uid":138252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:20:52.000Z","msg":"死仆街老母 我老母都係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52bf6f6c4109f8b27188eb204c183ccd6abac95d","tid":524344,"uid":90802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be2145367fe3f6f665271ee371906c08e964cd65","tid":524344,"uid":7878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"你有細佬？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"201